<plot>Final Fantasy Origins is a compilation of the first two Final Fantasy games. In the original Final Fantasy, four fated warriors must battle to save their world from destruction by bringing light back to the four crystals they bear. In Final Fantasy II, friends orphaned by war join a resistance to stop an evil empire from taking over the world. Each game has been given a visual and audio facelift, as well as a few gameplay tweaks to bring them closer in line with later titles in the series, such as Final Fantasy IV.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?194743</url></doc>
